title: The Fugitive S02E25 May God Have Mercy with Barry Morse Intro Di
description:
The Fugitive
S02E25
May God Have Mercy

Includes a video introduction by Barry Morse

One of 15 episodes from Season Two which have not been released on DVD
Remastered audio and video from VHS
Original music, not a synthesized replacement track

Airdate: March 16, 1965

The police are notified after Vic Leonetti (Telly Savalas) spots Kimble---whom Leonetti has long held responsible for the death of his child. 

Kimble: David Janssen. Anne: Carol Rossen. Cermak: Norman Fell. Gerard: Barry Morse.
